\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13261201\charrsid13261201 A very large percentage of postcards mailed in this theater reveal location directly or indirectly. 
Although these are now stopped, as far as possible, it is probable that in this and various other ways the locations of many units in this theater have already been made known.
\par 
\par Air Corps mail, increasingly routed through this office, is found to have 
an unusually high percentage of minor violations. Most of these violations have to do with locality, some also with details of equipment and operations. It appears that many Air Corps officers have not received adequate instructions in security regulation
s.
\par 
